msgstr "Журналирование с целью обнаружения атак и противодействия им"

# 26bf97860f2642478ea71bae38cbe263
#: ../../c9-implement-security-logging-monitoring.rst:31
msgid ""
"Use logging to identify activity that indicates that a user is behaving "
"maliciously. Potentially malicious activity to log includes:"
